latestPosts.caption:
#ELLEImpact: Sanjana Sanghi’s (@sanjanasanghi96) rise to fame has been nothing short of extraordinary. From her early days as a child actor to becoming one of Bollywood’s most promising young stars, she has consistently captivated audiences with her talent and grace. Known for her debut in ‘Dil Bechara’ opposite Sushant Singh Rajput, Sanjana has since carved a space for herself not only in films, but also as a vocal advocate for social causes like youth education and empowerment. This, combined with her commitment to her craft, makes her a true force to be reckoned with in the entertainment industry. Head to the 🔗 bio to read more.
____________________________
On @sanjanasanghi96: Nappa leather crunch jacket and flowing shiny shirt, both by @massimodutti. Amelia set skirt by @ivoryrose.in. (Image 1) Shankh earrings by @the.olio.stories. Ella rings by @zohra_india. (Image 2) Olivia mini sling by @irth_houseoftitan. (Image 1)

latestPosts.caption:
Trying to dress up and show up at your bestfriend's destination wedding looks a little bit like :

- Getting 10 minutes to change your outfit ( 🥵 )
- the girls stealing each other's make up and steam irons and hair irons 
- the boys being taught how to click acceptable photos while yelling "hurry up" on repeat 
- you looking at your outfits and feeling grateful for finally being smart about ditching the heels and picking the lightest most functional pieces so you can dance endlessly 😇 

#IKYK
